{
  "stem": "23942.7",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Most of the night we didn't sleep because we-- we-- we-- we told-- talked to each other what we went through.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "She went through very different than I did.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I realized I wasn't the only child that I survived such terrible, went through such-- she went through even more amazing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I realized that I was-- that I-- whatever she went through is even more amazing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we talked and talked and talked.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the morning, I realized this is it, that I'm never going to run.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And in the morning, I was given soap and a towel-- the first time my own soap and my own towel.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Felt good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I can wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I had to go through the rigors of what everybody-- you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Washing my face, brushing my teeth, getting my own soap, and going-- living like a normal human being.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The first time, like a normal child.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I didn't feel like a child anymore, but I-- I had to start re-- resuming the role of a child, what I was, a 12-year-old.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And there were various ages there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there-- we had-- there was a few rooms, bedrooms, and-- and-- and I remember there was an office and there was the lady one day called me in.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And she said, if you want, you can pick up this telephone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I felt very special, because nobody else was called in this office, all by myself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And she said to me, sit down, please.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Very nice, very polite and very-- she knew how to talk to a girl like me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Somehow she made a good impression.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And she wasn't like-- sometimes, you know, I met some people, they talked, like, superior.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But she was very nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "She didn't talk like a superior.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
